Fantastic content. Please equalize the volume levels for lessons throughout the specialization. I had to constantly re-adjust the volume for low volume lessons, then got blasted by decibels when the next lesson immediately after that was already recorded at a high volume. Had to play this game of "volume cat and mouse" throughout the specialization and it detracted from some of my learning enjoyment.  Thank you!
Love the short videos, reading materials, great course!
